				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/D%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-ch%C3%A2n/poem-hH1oWE-PPDL8pLuYpCiYHQ">Dưỡng chân - 養真</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Long-H%E1%BA%A1m-s%C6%A1n/poem-fqHLjf4dZWuh1YxFjTF8Dw">Đề Long Hạm sơn - 題龍頷山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Anh-T%C3%B4ng/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-3_0Jxe6Uqa9xxqhYqat1AA">Đông cảnh - 冬景</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Anh-T%C3%B4ng/author-YFBCcaKGsPA7uILcS-B8_Q">Trần Anh Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/L%E1%BA%A1c-S%C6%A1n-l%E1%BB%AF-trung/poem-C0ZGl5IED9tH5gTNABS2Cg">Lạc Sơn lữ trung - 樂山旅中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Minh/Minh-nguy%E1%BB%87t-thi%C3%AAn/poem-lWjx7gANwYrCP9tvHkwUbw">Minh nguyệt thiên - 明月篇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Minh/author-wg6EAaIQ8OL-TAAIuNs-Kg">Hà Cảnh Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/Ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Thi%C3%AAn-V%E1%BB%B1c-giang-hi%E1%BB%83u-ph%C3%A1t/poem-ZgkhBu5i-K5Jy7peW94bxA">Ngự chế Thiên Vực giang hiểu phát - 御制天域江曉發</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/Qu%C3%A1-Thu%C3%BD-%C3%81i-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-Ti%E1%BB%81n-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-phu-nh%C3%A2n/poem-B69w8S3mQB0g9JSCS2HgWg">Quá Thuý Ái điếu Tiền Trạch phu nhân - 過翠靄吊前擇夫人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khang-Th%C3%A0nh/Th%C3%A1i-li%C3%AAn-kh%C3%BAc/poem-4e3D3YYgDF9C6DYwO3SQhg">Thái liên khúc - 採蓮曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khang-Th%C3%A0nh/author-ReTo32Ylx4hiUvEOYxfkfA">Lý Khang Thành</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/T%E1%BB%8Bch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BA%B7ng-bi%E1%BB%87t-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Zv95G-n5SwCXXiF5RW2HkQ">Tịch thượng đại nhân tặng biệt kỳ 2 - 席上代人贈別其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Y%C3%AAm/T%C3%B4-m%E1%BA%A1c-gi%C3%A0/poem-bF2hymwy-OyotYa-NKGX3w">Tô mạc già - 蘇幕遮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Y%C3%AAm/author-V2PfiYxdyB2eEu42wOrwSw">Phạm Trọng Yêm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
